            <opener>
                <dateline>
                    <name type="place">540 E. 155<hi rend="underline">th</hi>
                        <unclear reason="illegible" cert="low" resp="#smb">In</unclear> New York<ptr target="loc.03192_n1"/></name>
                </dateline>
                <salute>Dear W.:</salute>
            </opener>
            <p>The letter, you sent me, was from your French admirer
                    Sarrazin,<ptr target="n3115"/> who will soon publish an essay on L. o. G. in one
                    of his books. Of the 'Grashalme'<ptr target="loc.05150_n2"/> I, so far, rec'd only <hi rend="underline">one</hi> copy, but expect some more. I hope, the book will be
                received favorably by the critics.</p>
            <closer>
                <salute>Yours ty</salute>
                <signed>Karl Knortz</signed>
            </closer>
